          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1303.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (or griddle if you have one) over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>brioche rolls</strong> in half</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>brioche</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 3 min or until toasted and charred, then set them aside until serving and save the pan for later</p>",
